name: Bond
description:
A beautiful bond created by like minded souls . Staying for each other through thick and thin and being each other’s greatest supporters and critic.
Friendship .
We all have souls we meet in our life for a period of time who become the best for us in that period maybe during school, office or even for a few days and they leave or go into silence but those moments created and cherished are always bliss and lucky are the ones who get to have that idiot or idiots for lifetime with the same energy as they met forever.
